      "description": "Overlay jellyoffice room temperature with the hottest node_exporter hwmon temperature per jelly host. Use 24h/7d ranges to see whether room warmth leads host thermal rise. Host series use max hwmon, so they are a practical hottest-sensor proxy rather than strict CPU-only temperature."
